<div class="space-y-5">
  <div>
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">Public Description</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-primary/70">This description will be included in the announcement that goes out to all volunteer drivers.</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-primary/70">Consider including:</p>
    <ul class="mt-1 list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-primary/70 space-y-0.5">
      <li>Information about the rider's English ability and native language</li>
      <li>The nature of the appointment (medical, legal, errand, etc.)</li>
      <li>Approximate duration of the appointment</li>
      <li>Whether the driver needs to wait or can leave and return</li>
      <li>Number of passengers, and whether any are children — the rider must provide car seats if necessary</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <%= render ride_description_public_field %>
</div>
